  "texts": [
    "Due to the abundance of available data, obtaining insights into a business and accurately predicting its performance can be challenging, especially when considering complicated factors involved in the business operating, e.g.",
    "products, human resources, market, investment, management etc.",
    "In this paper, we review important features and create a framework for modeling and predicting business success.",
    "A unique component of our work is the investment-businessmarket framework which characterizes three major key components related to the business.",
    "Based on this framework, our survey further outlines various features and models related to the business success prediction."
  ],
